<p>But, <em>don't</em> actually create a project! Instead, send <code>null</code> for the <code>projectId</code>.
Since starting a battle against <em>nothing</em> is nonsense, assert that 400 is the response
status code. This follows the pattern we did before in <code>ProgrammerControllerTest</code>.</p>
